{"entries":[{"id":"tsk-gen-24-2","title":"Genesis 24:2","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":2,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":2},"content":"<p>Beer-sheba. 21:31; 46:1; Jud 20:1</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-7","title":"Genesis 24:7","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":7,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":7},"content":"<p>That thou wilt. Heb. If thou shalt, etc. not. 11,14,15 the blessed. 12; 12:2; 21:22; 22:17; 24:31; Ps 115:15</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-12","title":"Genesis 24:12","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":12,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":12},"content":"<p>Which. 6:2; 27:46; 28:1,2,8 grief of mind. Heb. bitterness of spirit.</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-22","title":"Genesis 24:22","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":22,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":22},"content":"<p>hairy man. 25:25</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-32","title":"Genesis 24:32","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":32,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":32},"content":"<p>his hands. 16 he blessed. Ro 9:11,12; Heb 11:20</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-37","title":"Genesis 24:37","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":37,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":37},"content":"<p>Let people. 9:25,26; 22:17,18; 49:8-10; 2Sa 8:1-18; 10:1-19; 1Ki 4:21; Ps 2:6-9 Ps 72:8; Isa 9:7; Da 2:44,45; Re 19:16 be lord. 37; 25:22,23,33; 2Sa 8:14; 1Ki 11:15,16; 22:47; 1Ch 5:2 2Ch 25:11-14; Ps 60:1-12; *title Ps 60:2-12; Isa 63:1-6; Mal 1:2-5; Ro 9:12 cursed. 12:3; Nu 22:11,12; 23:8; 24:9; Zep 2:8,9; Mt 25:40,45</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-42","title":"Genesis 24:42","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":42,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":42},"content":"<p>19-23; 2Ki 10:19; Job 13:7; Mal 2:10; Ro 3:7,8; 2Co 4:7; 1Th 4:6</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-47","title":"Genesis 24:47","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":47,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":47},"content":"<p>hated. 4:2-8; 37:4,8; Eze 25:12-15; 35:5; Am 1:11,12; Ob 1:10-14 1Jo 3:12-15 The days. Ge 35:29; 50:3,4,10,11; De 34:8; 2Ch 35:24; Ps 35:14 then. 32:6; 2Sa 13:28,29; Ps 37:12,13,16; 140:4,5; 142:3; Pr 1:12,13,16 Pr 6:14; Ec 7:9; Ob 1:10; Eph 4:26,27; Tit 1:15,16; 3:3; 1Jo 3:12-15</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-57","title":"Genesis 24:57","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":57,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":57},"content":"<p>Esau. 27:33 Thou. 1</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-62","title":"Genesis 24:62","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":62,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":62},"content":"<p>he dreamed. 15:1,12; 20:3,6,7; 37:5-11; 40:1-41:57; Nu 12:6; Job 4:12-21 Job 33:15,16; Da 2:1-49; 4:1-37; 7:1; Mt 1:20; 2:12,13,19; Heb 1:1 ladder. 32:1,2; 2Ch 16:9; Isa 41:10; Joh 1:51; 2Ti 4:16,17; Heb 1:14</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-24-67","title":"Genesis 24:67","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":24,"verseStart":67,"chapterEnd":24,"verseEnd":67},"content":"<p>rose up. 22:3; Ps 119:60; Ec 9:10 and took.The practice of setting up stones as a memorial by travellers still exists in Persia, and other parts of the East.</p>\n<p>set it. 31:13,45; 35:14,20; Jos 24:26,27; 1Sa 7:12; 2Sa 18:18; Isa 19:19 poured. Le 8:10-12; Nu 7:1</p>"}]}